flowchart TD
    A[Input: User Preferences] --> B[Load songs from songs.csv]
    B --> C[For each song in catalog]
    C --> D[Genre match? +2 points]
    D --> E[Mood match? +1 point]
    E --> F[Compute numeric closeness scores]
    F --> G[Add weighted feature points]
    G --> H[Store final score for song]
    H --> I{More songs left?}
    I -- Yes --> C
    I -- No --> J[Sort songs by score descending]
    J --> K[Select Top K recommendations]
    K --> L[Output recommended songs]